DWM

Anforderungen:

- Color Scheme (gruvbox, .Xresource)
- Keybindings
	1. Software:
		* Terminal mod+enter
		* Scratchpad Terminal Toggle mod+shift+enter
		* Browser mod+b
		* Mail mod+m
		* Calendar mod+c
		* News/RSS mod+n
		* Torrent mod+t
		* Music Player mod+p
		* File Manager mod+shift+f
	2. Shortcuts
		* Program Launcher (dmenu) mod+d
		* Mounting MTP mod+f3
		* Mouting USB mod+f4
		* Mounting Network
		* Display Select mod+f5
		* Logoff, Shutdown, Restart (dmenu) mod+shift+e
		* Lock Screen (slock, i3lock) ctrl+alt+del/mod+shift+x
		* Refresh DWM (i.e. after recompile) mod+shift+r
	3. Media Buttons
		* Volume up, down, mute (multimedia buttons)
		* Screen Brightness up/down (display buttons)
		* Toggle Touchpad (touchpad button)
		* Media Player Play, Pause, Stop, Next, Prev (multimedia buttons)
	5. Layout Control
		* Master/Slave mod+z
		* Centered Master mod+u
		* Floating mod+i
		* Monocle mod+o
		* Fib Spiral mod+shift+z
		* Centered Floating Master mod+shift+u
		* Bottom Stack mod+shift+i
		* Fib Dwindle mod+shift+o
	4. Tag Control
		* Switch Tags 1-9 mod+1-9
		* Move Client to Tag 1-9 mod+shift+1-9
		* Toggle Tag 1-9 mod+ctrl+1-9
		* Toggle Client to Tag 1-9 mod+ctrl+shift+1-9
		* Show all Tags (Tag 0) mod+0
		* Append Client to All Tags (Tag 0) mod+shift+0
	5. Client Control
		* Switch to Fullscreen
		* Kill Client
		* Toggle Floating
		* Toggle Client to Master
		* Focus Through Stack
		* Move through stack (master, slave)
		* Resize Master Stack
	6. Display Control
		* Switch to Display
		* Move Tag too other Display
